Source: <a href="https://developers.google.com/search/docs/crawling-indexing/mobile/mobile-sites-mobile-first-indexing">Google Search Central</a>, 2024</p>
<p>Since July 2024, Google crawls and indexes the mobile version of every site first. If your mobile experience is poor, your rankings suffer across all devices.</p>
<p><strong>44. Pages in the top 5 Google results score an average of 70+ on mobile page speed tests.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/page-speed-seo/">Ahrefs</a>, 2024</p>
